    "poemName": "The Burial of Herr Fischer VI",
    "poemAuthor": "Zekiah",
    "poemContent": {
        "type": "fragment",
        "styles": [],
        "children": [
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Die Gesundheit hath toll,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "As the bloody bell strikes 9,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "It's a systematic tall, evenly spaced,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Each ring, marking th' upcoming hour of death,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "\"Here lies Herr Fischer VI\""
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "What a man you are,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Stratified crowds gather, people clumping,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "By matter of thought, how to make it appear,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "To be, fair, but of bias,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Randomness creates a chaos,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Entropy crackles in the air..."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Again the bloody bell tolls, now it is midnight."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Mitternacht, the dead cry,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "As the city turns silent, it's empty cities weep silently,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "At this newfound threat,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "All lies silent, a part from the forest path,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "That leads into that dense undergrowth,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Few words remained in these lands,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "The mines had long fell silent, emitting a dull bloody glow."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "A crimson sky revealed itself overhead, only those of the"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Forest dared walk, among those twigs, red in hue,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Bones and skulls of dead beasts,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "But back at the capital, as again the dock whirs,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "The streets awaken in fear, met by the blighted hearse,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Through interlocking valleys of architecture, menaced in design,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "And through the bloody views of the streets,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Atop that carnage was a man, clad in feather,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Deathly plague-doctor"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "And he said to me:"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "\"It's a descendant of the late lineage of Fischer,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "The infamous family, yet I scorn my kind, and"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Weep for the students at the academy."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "I storm them all, sane my liege, who I bear,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "From the merciless upper-course down to the gentle but deep,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Lands of the low, I have carried this hearse,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "A coffin bearer, for seven days yet,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "My journey plotted in the bag of blood running up my spine,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Continuous was the toil, yet the event of this day,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "If I may say so discretely,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "It be a terrible day für die Geselschaft,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "For now will I bury Herr Fischer VI,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "The only honourable of his line, though bred from menaces,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "He fought to free the scholars of Tibbet from their unending curse,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Now again, I recount, as this bloody moon low-lies,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "I am a bearer of a curse."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "The curse to think of the crimes of the Fischers, evermore,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Despite this fellow, blighted by the plague,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "As I, indeed am one infected."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Now nam'd the doctor of physique,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "A plague doctor, who wanders these harmed streets,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Now peace, I say to you, and I bid you well\"."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "The doctor was ne'er seen again,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "As the dawn approached."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Another day, another folk."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "This was the tale of Herr Fischer VI,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "In this torn, where he was carried, already dead"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "This torn, pained in it's bloody coat."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 3
            }
        ]
    },
    "pageStyle": "centre",
    "pageBackground": ""
}